net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.util

Class GridObjectiveProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.strategy.util.GridObjectiveProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC

    public class GridObjectiveProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.sf.jclec.JCLEC
    Auxiliary class for GrEA algorithm. This class represents the grid properties of an objective (lower and upper boundaries and width) divided in grids.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    GrEA, Serialized Form
